Text: OMG! Now this is a RARE find. Digidesign doesn't even have this on their site anymore. It's discontinued. Will seed...

DO THIS BEFORE YOU INSTALL!!!!!!!

Don't forget, if your running XP, Vista, Windows 
7. You need to 

- Right click ProToolsFree501
- Go to Properties
- Click on "Compatibility" Tab
- Check the "Run this program in compatibility mode for"
- In the drop menu, select Windows 98 / Windows ME.
- Now you may install the program
- If it still wont go through, right click the install file and select "Run as Administrator"
